Collection: users
- Each user document needs an added field called "role" with the value of either "student" or "instructor"

Collection: courses
-Each course document must have the following fields:
    -dates
        -this is a map
        -must include a field called "start" that is a date
    -image
        -this is a string of the src
    -instructors
        -this is an array of strings
        -each string contains an instructor name for the course
    -name
        -this is a string that tells the name of the course

-Each course document must have the following collections:
    -lesson
        -where each document includes the following fields: 
            -an array called participatingStudents
            -time
                -this is a date
